data.description: Nestled in the friendly amenity filled Somersby neighborhood, this spacious 4-bedroom, 2 ½ - bathroom home boasts serene screen room in a private fenced in yard that backs up to the woods, perfect for both privacy and outdoor enjoyment. Step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan, seamlessly blending living, dining, and kitchen areas. The heart of the home, the kitchen, features SS appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar. The large owner's suite is a true retreat, offering a generous space to relax and unwind. The on-suite bathroom is a spa-like oasis, complete with a luxurious soaking tub and a separate shower. With three additional bedrooms, PLUS a bonus/playroom there's plenty of room for a growing family or guests. Plus, the second bathroom ensures everyone has their own space. This house is not just a place to live; it's a HOME. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours!
